{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"502ae59e33","title":"国务院外事办公室、中央宣传部关于纪念孙中山诞生一百周年宣传规格的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d22e8ba00f","index":0,"year":1966,"month":11,"day":10,"articleId":"502ae59e33","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"周总理","id":"838b5f2c9d","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"b7a1c99161","name":"国务院"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b46d25d83b","type":"title","text":"国务院外事办公室、中央宣传部关于纪念孙中山诞生一百周年宣传规格的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"502ae59e33","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f7ae669e3e","type":"paragraph","text":"外办发〔66〕94号","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"502ae59e33","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8225c4261a","type":"paragraph","text":"现将纪念孙中山诞生一百周年宣传规格通知你们，请照此执行。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"502ae59e33","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eeca8a2656","type":"paragraph","text":"一、主席如为孙中山诞生一百周年纪念题字，全国各报一律刊登。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"502ae59e33","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bc986c43f6","type":"paragraph","text":"二、全国各报发表首都纪念大会的新闻。首都和上海、南京广州报纸同时刊登首都纪念大会上董副主席的开幕词和周总理、宋副主席、何香凝的讲话。其他省市报纸，如版面拥挤，可先登董副主席的开幕词和总理讲话，然后再发表其他人讲话。上海、南京、广州的纪念活动，由新华社发综合消息。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"502ae59e33","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4db2299637","type":"paragraph","text":"三、人民日报发表纪念社论，各省、市、自治区报纸转载。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"502ae59e33","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"46301baf29","type":"paragraph","text":"四、全国各报在第一版发表由新华社提供的六寸孙中山半身照片。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"502ae59e33","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cc05a8685d","type":"paragraph","text":"五、人民日报发表程潜、邵力子、熊克武写的纪念文章，各地报纸不转载。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"502ae59e33","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c7788ae5e2","type":"paragraph","text":"六、中央人民广播电台和北京电视台播送首都和上海、南京、广州纪念会的新闻。中央人民广播电台播送首都纪念大会上的讲话，不作实况广播。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"502ae59e33","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"673707017b","type":"paragraph","text":"七、由新闻电影制片厂拍一小型彩色纪录片。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"502ae59e33","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ea6372b8eb","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：根据文件原件打印","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"502ae59e33","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}